huhaRjB_eWi6OQScvvt0xJWdLllWfXYxdOUjpnQj7SO-0fkhu3CXWYk7aqA3qh1WEGMNpA7tx28zX0cIkgfEXw2D8gl2NYTbRGnknFWs4-Rlsp2Jgx9M2vtLXzvx-NzvpBWjIcOyM45R92TaC_whJsoJJ3o-t_Mx74/_Coseh2etDYiKsciz_Pt_sudWquYBClW/7" rel="nofollow" target="_blank"&gt;&lt;img border="0" src="https://sli.bloomberg.com/imp?s=1148994&amp;amp;li=13161973&amp;amp;m=d42b0cd27465a66be4227a135cb7a14e&amp;amp;p=04082025&amp;amp;lctg=8b37da73-f2d1-4a1c-8a9f-cb9d10343de6&amp;amp;stpe=default&amp;amp;li_coord=mobile&amp;amp;collapse_width=550" style="display: block !important; width: 100% !important;" width="550" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt; &lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;!--&lt;![endif]--&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style="border-collapse: collapse;"&gt;&lt;table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px;" width="100%"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style="border-collapse: collapse; padding: 0px 10px;"&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;随着纳斯达克100号&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/qq1_sw9q_xcJpXgo1C_b2WfmTRlMwHA91j3VX-YHCJn_yq2opQPkdap-wCzxrWDv2dA3JIyIySTAUnJKk7-tr4r0GceCfTeQ7FYbLrJsi6ldDJytJfjNYk2MHmPHW9Iz_7HF9f7rTn8zCqDwz3dMxtfPPzar2EiQhDCNazedjbmStFZXgZM89HsOYqb1wpEODHRdsm2bHgxUXw3JANZFKMMtPmlxb4v72PjjSgS6NSh_27gitPSyXQwcp1B1bCYCw3Ti5U_Gt684I70YrtZjvXJXuU3h7tmUnv-zU51Z8vvwXO7X0mg-OCzuQ8Zk0NKqXF0UIGQDiy-fxayukk5OYtkjTBoiChtmp9yysQxXMyuNpzvoE5lRCc0Gow/k23gJxoGnVwcdvay06jLfYhLG_j1-Sg3/7" target="_blank"&gt;已经&lt;/a&gt;进入熊市，很快可能是标准普尔500指数。随着美国和中国之间的来回贸易威胁，野外挥舞&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/Ey0bGw8NT-xBf_MD-qIySkFL4BM4lzcKVf-C16Wg8fLTHgRtBwywmePf0_-pMWuOWMzlnLPwgIKC9334WDaq-MtKreHGbdaE6_j9zweXSKq0Zff7DVZsi3yZCVYm4HZvce49MKVIgqYp1Khs-Ij6ke_i00wv-_YaJY9jc7VzKjyKcwKi6Foe2Ox75d2_MLdGmQb2Bm5Kd8ONi1qGCkRe5yBYxhZMNbtGnclKCIRjUU-4_tJQocxdBG-cP71bLftCNh-GRyC13JMv8sXrsFn_bLqUYLb7QviW8oHxyfB5-EuYPoHzYcBghydLqxPOPItJJ2n7DEKIVIaVU4M3DZa-5rTbcI5itaWlf5-IHHbQ3oVzLIK1QsiomjgZYA/OlZqXzyq1xk4a6ngR6K6P2UUpY_9JjKI/7" target="_blank"&gt;着华尔街进行了第四次会议，&lt;/a&gt;使股票降低了，在关税引起的屠杀三天后消除了早期的集会。标准普尔500指数下跌了近1.6％，将其放在熊国家的边界​​。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;当特朗普政府官员说，白宫对中国商品的关税越来越高，即使在北京发誓要“ &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/HKRwmd0atFc4K90xf8txZdh3DKskoK_krxTHMiKLk9RA0GobhquG68Rpmki29IXdYXPP2gtO8AfThPeGUxtqKccy0g1tGgJh2-EEA2pxbefdiJr-AcTjSaIonaYFnTQ5Wr2ljo_bPQ0UfgWasB8LY6EnEPP3YonU4367f-4pXq94tWh7OLSPy7NZtElWChnq62BinZW28fF8qn2ZIxxMLed2OPM5wZfw1geklYyjeQCLtqary0BIvoMJbelj_zpZpnJkNcIHIFgPOrsz2Hdc7QslfyAOSGaotB8hY82p-DoWlCuN3wwTHYf5UIfL5lvoRJT6zZ86vPhIMWFv5gVKSqUDGrbREGZnDdQAL1ajKpS0lTzF2kvHz_4Xog/i9Z78I4OcOt_yKJWUfegBV6llbNtp1cQ/7" target="_blank"&gt;战斗到最终&lt;/a&gt;”以回应美国总统唐纳德·特朗普的早期征收时，怀有对中国商品的征收更多的关税&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/YmqwX_La0CnXBNT0iEGnfv_r5oWm3qd26A4W1_qzaJ9D2jqQjBVd-2Z_eTyhdnX6PrEgNOj2dmdJe_ITNG60UGxCOcrpTkkOpiJAIit5BzPVAzQIaXX8Zmt_Zh-H5zZchu23YtAIforOcu2b0k1U10-5AX-w2aHBgMhUbxbLcdlYm8fzBTcsTN2xmHiqrYF1hHN5YMuzqsoY6zdKLQ_EY-_Tc-zv7yuBh-EcPC6ELslThAn--jNzxyRRmLE6eUF2V-u20mjuRrWYvpQHvFIltnK6Q_GWW_Ugi6d2nXcO5xDBlOiLIhO4xe_qHQgh-4KjltzeWwUlaIhThw0OLHp8Rc_hg9Zs_4G5q7gV1jjGCu1cqquXyq6V2WLRaQ/KAaclEe7aEiQKteRDqjEvTkJ_Is5BA2j/7" target="_blank"&gt;（即使在中国商品的高达104％&lt;/a&gt; ）上向前迈出的希望，这一希望迅速结束了极端波动。股票继续潜水，因为中国总理李·齐安（Li Qiang）表示，他的国家拥有充分的政策工具来“完全抵消”负面的外部冲击。随着贸易商提高了对美联储削减税率的赌注，财政部两年的收益率跌落。标准普尔500指数结束了这一天，错过了一年的收益。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div class="body-image" style="margin: 20px 0px;"&gt; &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/UizLFgIJ_CrM0EUyPREN_ASCwrPJS8PJXhLPoobi33Z7-4uCnoMZbvAvM-imm-H7PntEYw5AR3E2fFETDcJXuBKe4CSEmXlcvJs26NzzYWPmW-bMgdnaLxJN31iNU3b-r48c4kY5UQs92x4-abkAnPZiDfwBmNXut7GPX8wEz9PyhEX3dk3BhXpjhXm-lkA2SQqqf3dUKFKn41InXqEkJ4xa0PpYxlXZRrMfDUbfAQqf-uCEc0z9KcNN88tvqG7WeRypL4a8aEazYkNb8ThsfOoMZXvaIoki0n4k7jSWZh49BZT0H8jEJ_B8Oe_Yyp28BiNQLvkXFsgYqNqk86yC1JDNVtg8NWiM2PWEi92HfkAb-eL94zy3MbGBBw/f1nM_0nEN4J3dZKzudSuDYGsLnMw3wZF/7" target="_blank"&gt;&lt;!--[if mso]&gt;&lt;table width="550"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td&gt;&lt;img alt="" src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iQXSV6reX5WA/v3/pidjEfPlU1QWZop3vfGKsrX.ke8XuWirGYh1PKgEw44kE/-1x-1.png" width="550"/&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt; &lt;div style="display:none"&gt;&lt;![endif]--&gt;&lt;img alt="" src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iQXSV6reX5WA/v3/pidjEfPlU1QWZop3vfGKsrX.ke8XuWirGYh1PKgEw44kE/-1x-1.png" style="display: block; width: 530px; margin: auto;" /&gt;&lt;!--[if mso]&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;![endif]--&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;同时，在华盛顿，民主党参议员罗恩·怀登（Ron Wyden）表示&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/1hwqawfkvdmnFzX5unsExWA0xkNOhSZMc9u1Xnd9fXgDWZtROAKZSY6kmDSZ6ucMznfWVzf3vqker_BbP71E6qQaQToZ65L4gROX8QFaFqVeXDW9UTPaM22_qQ4LchD3F-Ah8LpadfCfXVMP_6wtR9fZrYprDzAF8FqNF5zppSW20Djn1OMoQmrdPNF4bFP7qBjiTDOBoYNnDxl23E9gxC23_9noc3tPICZgejb-qLeSzmP32YRI-8OayXb851yTTLux-pKRLZZfy6PGz5KLy3qq-3n6e3ckCaEJt8YUqJB-PZQ-TU3kSMMS5sfbTR4l6OMHIjKduI06Xgdc_gi_wl8NxFD4_VyqLOhsMoxNe7COXWZ74LK1opu5KPM/xMbmNcRdwL1Q2cc3m7uEX1G9i9OyhT8B/7" target="_blank"&gt;，他将对废除关税进行投票，&lt;/a&gt;以测试共和党对特朗普贸易战的政治支持。怀登（Wyden）的gambit将要求共和党人对关税攻势进行公开立场，这&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/z5VoZVgfydS8o3CDpfnN2uW005q6mmhd8MY3luTdmUFWVNEzFqi47Ox0CddDhkYGn0ZgrIUTeBoaVh_IkPfMqyLisjwXOYdQ9wwlPHmCXKmosDvuYsHN-KBYuzZ64BmgI9hdKju6gFitxci4OlzMoY6gVddczSyHpnVvhWD_2yoluBsFIIdaJki2wZIcOvAy1mAhqd6Qhx_wEGHToWRwiFczcXTzTWfYx6msq91uN3Zr7O1-ZDPwAFWNeiQUuZ6UY8PgW64OnuZqjXvIHMv10Uru3nBEYvk-gWj8hHq5jIgMAnhtLqhKwfQQ98LTBPFwxsAdwEJeVMGUYF9JzhtMsIqqJyGXuVpHUahHBkb-vXdScZpnMeBDAxpex2g/IzPkF-grQ4RyW4XRuUG8vd5U5VzK5G3M/7" target="_blank"&gt;引起了人们对经济衰退和升高通货膨胀的担忧&lt;/a&gt;。共和党参议员通常很快向特朗普展示忠诚，开始对几个月前的损害造成的损害&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/QW7F_WVj0784s_WQKuHRbhREctBXuLvXO1ppEcMoqHV0-UCYAc9Xf8y6D5WTtP3IUYRQxt5cHtQl49fgbtJA8mbfxH6iGBPpKnlWOF8Gj5uLBQZNhhIB2MFsbi5L44ehWOxoS_2x4tfxkGaZVb-R9k0yft1LYHk8flqFOAF-hsgWV9uhdet4Im9Lsvb9XTMmYA5HFxZkyWgNwWnAVGFXfWzWfRYsvjyGORYE64FYKhDJ4pB-_TvKFchDLYhK_KIiYGa4yJQ3A-DlYxAEhQ45OKe6hyz3R19K1pdm8QMxhvm5FiWOfp0c3-VhXnNfLgnDREoKxHi3hblaNS0izgvgjqN2RcN36Cr_CZA7qfOH-t3DNMtTNCeUWXRZPdM/-OwgwdigamBke3yeQEj1JFMUpZQUCUfb/7" target="_blank"&gt;表现出不安的迹象，&lt;/a&gt;这是一种有韧性的经济，其就业强劲和通货膨胀下降。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt; “如果发现这是错的，我会cho绕谁的喉咙？”北卡罗来纳州的共和党参议员汤姆·蒂利斯（Thom Tillis）周二在参议院财政委员会听证会上问。&lt;em&gt;纽约时报&lt;/em&gt;的弗兰克·布鲁尼（Frank Bruni）最近称其为蒂利斯（Tillis），他投票决定了特朗普最极端的内阁选秀权，即“ &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/YFrbxgQWsm4ZignRuKuXUFWtl1Ux6Pa8qydGnlmcytuf7mCWIn0_G7ZyaYrIH0DHMzC51DFoZ4vC64-43Xymm7Vt2XOQsf5EYnbJ2JuCtWahR2diZf_MBzot3u6AmcK9VDpigRxVLL8zr8w6SueAOcBOvoOWRRmAHBcWnpIQs2ZrHZ5_RiFJN0EQav68Vp3JP0p1afz00lxaqR6CqgjTzN9hMzrV4g7oRvyq3W4F49vWqq4iaOhElYZc55sI0ZLfz1Lr2roLKkKgjORwbRY82h_Qg7sXSP5rwdow_L0uAn84MlbjgdSqLRdtyVA89NDckOs4hFaS8apTDV1AxN0Jx3zsKbjUuWqdpdGlhjP9lbXCa7gKYXcZhn8csHjyP7Zt5URT-djAKSqOdVg1NUaATU2_2qyfYLKskUAdO3kNGBDqpjP9IJAmd3ELISlsipclPLrdpOAmrMbFkbo0BuCIdzDtfp79AN9iP2OFisZugeGRWKwIFat2XSFtpPooaKsHmjjjr_4MdPiMJw/m3WlJ4QCYGwZ-7TZEqti8SBQQ5_kF06Z/7" target="_blank"&gt;道德愤怒的丹尼尔·戴·刘易斯（Daniel Day-Lewis&lt;/a&gt; ）”。但是，著名共和党参议员的公开警告可能会在党与其领导人的关系中得到一些新的事物。 &lt;span&gt;&lt;em&gt;- &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/K9Ym9JS-zkvdsOBO7DRk56COuyyoxqxBdU6zKAiIXNdQcj2331OcE7u3adInRQTlNivgKKM__tfU3_F9shduCUfLWQl-IF6TgcdxYP55vFqKKdimZwIB8Ru6PMzQXlW2d7kkThi4GCz8tN6nwzklAuIWxfAWmVb103grUq-y1mG1ujoKEVK6jVbt0UHCEvqGqYWwXBi81kZh9qAUHb5vmzdezhvjT-aophUPNZshNC58JzstKtCGdd8yFjCjTkHdm7Vx-opSympbA2LAjSqI9QLd7XxD3d6uUwSLYCD7AAg3nV9T6uuN-q1jgqM04eGYE9tqnHQsNraszF0V97sOZy02cWFr5FRR6q5hEulyd4a4vb4JURZZfQCxAj8/C57sqcaYwV6-pzL3HVv7O6sa2U03_qgf/7" target="_blank"&gt;乔丹·帕克（Jordan Parker Erb）&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;em&gt;从工厂到董事会等等， &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/lPak9jn1DTx8DntK3-efQq0fKIAMy5QLeG4kVEv5yzneqayRShqfaoBo_Bx1CQh6e