"font-style: italic; line-height: 1.44;"&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style="border-collapse: collapse; padding: 0px 10px;"&gt;&lt;table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="100%"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style="border-collapse: collapse;"&gt;&lt;h2&gt;来自绿色的更多信息&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style="border-collapse: collapse;"&gt;&lt;table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px;" width="100%"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style="border-collapse: collapse; padding: 0px 10px;"&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;还有另一个要考虑的关税影响： &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/s52l8Ad_ZUc1TmUIc8mNGduuWZ3IO8rbS1dQAg4T5C0ilDwuf_5eSGRahk3vFD2fbZmo7CKDC3bZooNQWQChNbKtk4Klhw2dMxZgQoAwQeF69WMVQyGlg8m_6Yz53_PXMpllk1Ap9OCod0L1ZZ4A3GYZ2EZ0GiJhC8PybRRswUfZc-MwPcdAvxuTrBPOwQUZ8MYdXJHDXFYXKi9uZUH_VIJZUKIf54NAnr4g1obAqi8KyVEc6tYnTt6i4-4JccxpXjsqvl8sQO2TNbpgseu6fEcSwuhoQcb5OJO0VacSE1Hda0F_e-p0tIAF43zW6CfPGQzM8CWhE_zaIxoHVNU98czBumSInw0NdhvIUDFstP19wqIuir-s4DC83sI/c8bruwJX_PYlXuk-jQuIRWbzK7CyHkeV/7" target="_blank"&gt;房屋保险费率&lt;/a&gt;。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt; &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/t-IDLV14lU0Te0NDGpWLDPkrrvfW5jodQbcs690te4MsqcYNQ8dWdMvrJS2eRChIpOLzUBMvNePtC7a7uCbtt316KhH0af25KqXw10TgymhW_CH7ZptFFlKHkQxE0eny_Yg5kbz5BnkCSItyrJ2zbZDgWVip4RWo7sx1o4ZHOeeTlzH_9jW4OxWWiT6YCL66LzDOAxXrUFibqJuU4liT5bRfEbm2_MSIkgSW7d9DnRZWCk8STpApKCkhAqCKzDVRunzvjj7BheZP6_ckNPc5ALmJUcuUebasJul_g_Fqzn_tjCVbG0lSe4UzpREFPZZhoSIHefed88ADAvXMB7I7rZcp0NtlQP5sAwgkwx3jcryjcDLFWC4apcYmLW4/yvD12eJL4JzLx9uQilT9Ej7Xm80ttg7M/7" target="_blank"&gt;在气候灾难之后重建房屋&lt;/a&gt;的成本将增加，因为预计关税会促进建筑材料的成本。新报告的作者Matt Brannon说，这反过来可能会进一步提高保险费率。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;预计到年底，全国范围内的&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/LgjG0WO_CJFPKGo5R74AYgqoVZIo734qd38KpMXnwChv3HI774zVPttLV8noeAVo8rxrOCzGt-9IimZofhQcuriv3Fs1N8j99X84pgY0ke8aEkVKb4LQfNtDzImeA0tY2i3V55dD9UUgsPndwwgCaxzGxNYL4AfabM5Hw_sfJvKTuuj-UZChqRKh2paR63Psq3eu3pUXrox53zXmmFBHlahGuovgUxyisOflkLnWCXnPe0YTS2809FoXIg8XgOuZ9dGHqTPEWZGnCzpK4DaApmxu4MBGwBFh4wMKmZ-iS7-ZyAQZOJ_RGhjDeiPifcwyr3zN6B0kRFnw0X-lkS7h6OEenmblXMHvvQgkCJ5xz1yE1a0E0mwgkURKbMI/hzEdQHTxo1K5KWKvvKvQMm9xE638efUf/7" target="_blank"&gt;房屋保险年度平均成本&lt;/a&gt;已经将增加8％，达到3,520美元，价值400,000美元的房屋。包括路易斯安那州，爱荷华州和明尼苏达州在内的一些州会看到两位数的增加。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div class="body-image" style="margin: 20px 0px;"&gt; &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/xTpNGwT5xD9N0b259H6B63A8Nx45yZpntCA6_J5BmY-aabUiw3QJhDmKJfMAC3WIh5LWL82FeXWgiHFOMfUI8q9kYEt0Zj_h7f9Do5WT17l-6c7NVd2FdsRF23cLtiRqbpAhnEnM_Z2YFnewR8hiRyGurquJMoZUkD4czxXojE7DGifQBiY_-b8awTNljcqYynADqd4u0zBR6-n24WrHz1aMMtR3kpiB0oxt6vRu8riO1sxAofcH0WYjf8V1jWsty41TMd9_LNKw1xQuVL8qeOAaBK7TL0uCoPc01RPSx5HcyHgzysLpHdrp-iv3l74SND9_Daczpnvi-d1GQwpVjZhOXzhVQSmnEtqQRhlPDj2fMjLwV2toOmYVT8M/QRrkElYALv7fDaDYjq7WZ9Jxpi-2s7cH/7" target="_blank"&gt;&lt;!--[if mso]&gt;&lt;table width="550"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td&gt;&lt;img alt="" src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iZFeRZD8vFqs/v3/pidjEfPlU1QWZop3vfGKsrX.ke8XuWirGYh1PKgEw44kE/-1x-1.png" width="550"/&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt; &lt;div style="display:none"&gt;&lt;![endif]--&gt;&lt;img alt="" src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iZFeRZD8vFqs/v3/pidjEfPlU1QWZop3vfGKsrX.ke8XuWirGYh1PKgEw44kE/-1x-1.png" style="display: block; width: 530px; margin: auto;" /&gt;&lt;!--[if mso]&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;![endif]--&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;&lt;strong style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;特朗普希望履行他对恢复煤炭的诺言。&lt;/strong&gt;唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）总统将&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/uTkq9AlKgQR7iChhARX91nkR5TigLlSEkfxs9FNGs0nvISWqC3aJ9wPBu22obEDz9hTyRBd5