;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/9BAAJEZ1pSaaYk_1AwuaGZOZ--HI2jzRqO7x9C5u1L7satGFYlWwORW_IZT1QGoyB5cRjMEM01CfmNnZwf2Ki0YK92hEsM4YT_vTOMSQipatPaoCD7UOo_iAIcl1lZ2BNNTixigs8S6KvR8jRyUYke7Yp5ZYy_OeejFyl6m1l2d_mwEFKsYJMVAghM2Zv7D5-0S6XVlP2xzzIpOS3rvLg479NPlsYvqhwhE2wpC746coU_4A1nu4AVgETfZgRydjknb8-jVe0tD0NEwGl_LJmQzbrFbhN3rq0Rs722EGqlepqey5gopFIUxHVDLeqDXRm1xB74Sm2_bfq9CSl1I3QcCkWVNRHn3gKODvnAfL2Z8Wn1YrbxyVK8Sekac/QuL52s9y4HC_FTmduosu1LzB7yXR6EI-/7" target="_blank"&gt;小丑表演&lt;/a&gt;”，他指出：“这不仅对市场和经济不利，而且对特朗普也很不利。”目前，有迹象表明，美国股票&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/IX2iUAky3Kfbs9bFJQ6eNaeag_d5gQw_jHoyx_iVHFM2oqJWWEKb5mh8d4Qy1GYhtca0G9UZ8WI6hO7lce4DXl9dChwIojWMWJQf6k3cjnYFdGvZIydBp0qRSiQbKMYgLxF7qK4PZXdX_7PXBFHc48VEeHotPLlQ3wJoXDLF392sQtCgRTFn8h4xkTZDyLeoPpD62l-lrHOHQxrr-JSB4KDMo9qRKGkdiLvUoty97-IqAJ5BoylaDs2tCrfKMBH70VRJOanTVsMyWz6UdKshX9t3v9n7lasUL6ca8Q_rqK1Jq5nUMqJlscIYb7VrMd0sLdrbCVdNBUwvKGrzY2JpxM9BRP0888kFOxyCGX3BYM9YDqPW8wcUJJdiPzA/4ujks06qPWWh1slWtp0My0X4txdZ3NMB/7" target="_blank"&gt;有望进行适度的篮板&lt;/a&gt;。&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;strong style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;中国发誓&lt;/strong&gt;要在与美国的贸易战争中“ &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/_Y0DwQPoKBToYFZr_WTCC-dEsxOUAvBrIQ8JFm60wmOCSi_tufUm9DnlYfeNBYRa_qYq56hAU1NnOwc7VwJpTuBEKF_UxuAHrPArw9MuU64JO-HotEuhVRh0b-7WgMXQvTsfwRudWfqDEC7qKOCQlVvP8xWiilqlPU0zDPprFvig9FiYLTZVHKAZQrDGRHGh9PFCJSQa3ClDOeHTwhDip4neoAXDXpSxUrmKvOsaX2CNMIHSVHuKBS2TBjQam1ySPGtBVjxCBFXs2YHf3N71eLP2ZxiHKJSStHkQcoV9idUuaZcHYIvRsPQCAY9FryaL3bC55KG-EcsTZpHGTq5QnrPS3o02o0jX5jZD3grDVcaZ7h7xofAnzH87gwk/fJt84syxXOD6AONX_JqiEb0lx68tzfn5/7" target="_blank"&gt;战斗&lt;/a&gt;”，这增加了世界上两个最大经济体之间长期而令人衰弱的山雀战役的风险。美国财政部长斯科特·贝森特（Scott Bessent）表示，不进行报复的贸易伙伴可能会降低关税率，而且&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/nIef-hxcCSyK1KMM5FJEqstYBEoOvoiGeUow78G6u72tjt0Qu3HJ0znjzod0rMBvtDjPJzondd1UQm-wCsJvx4S5NgtdEXMBY1LV1fj0Mo4cnzwCEM7LGlRD6XufnX7GIfD2oadMmbPuY0-Wi8EwQ7mPR0DWmusGknxClKPmiJlN9P2E-ttiL-lQolm68hSBE