;Google介绍了人工智能生成的&lt;/strong&gt;答案及其搜索算法的更改导致独立网站的&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/MJN6vINzN5Yy_c5JdnBcUwk5z2xVqWUfP2VHeIKV3B9jiWuImbXOSwqnSJKRYNBX2xGl74WDpL5NTXn2fETbR04ok1DK_dl-lBy0jf5ptdB95anQfDmgUejOMyZrHHcrWCYMs2_EBMNIDLHGIcRXZZQtTg6jTIRl_ePLIXW8yR-GdR6O3uWdKYFs3glazQnGPd7Blth7xId_aIsX3ANqjzHwta6hFQWrTiycsv7uKBTGrpCeVnd8FIAdaZqtDv3bMFph2B0U0ayDYGIw3bJczZ7xnQJRPp1gQeqo_qqCU7Fgl4hJSv4eW8tH3g9yN0R9tw7kWMrxA2ZB96l7JyxzCgkMq6ogMbKHUXPnjkSNi5ddv7ESaAQGygYjWdw/6XzGzX78ymXomMZ7OWUZJgqKtDS5f8Mp/7" target="_blank"&gt;流量大幅下降&lt;/a&gt;，从而破坏了Google与内容创建者之间的共生关系。许多出版商报告说，流量下降了70％或以上，导致收入损失并迫使一些人关闭或重塑其发行策略，这最终可能会&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/ykXeAn_VchJB884VEaJ828Pr1wOmi8LaMc_iKKN_r41z-fbvbkT8aakE3QWf7H-2pp9cfzS1C8BVvzxZ2weJGoviprmb5TXt2g3H1Pey4_HYuR6yadvk_zeCQhwmtTLRrvmPdF8fMqMwjP_XyKbAEtTfV4E3T085GTTIRK2ZKrsBEyDCHcXdeOggZCevuLLkcqRnGtEUMC1GTDhUsNriEssCcp6y18tcgEYh96uB75iMwS5kLkbRG3qBDzORJzuGFiOds8XtO0soyPKVWwWFbEcQdIGe4n6j9WiO7pvmRX3baWcx6KrjQuSAYH53aE7tiKqHTVCb1JSA6I2WS6LoVpiUgZio-01qy-8QU1WAI399scG9XsYrAIs2tgc/GajTB9G_gv0DY-394C-LRmP1EzB4wHWd/7" target="_blank"&gt;降低Google可以访问的信息质量&lt;/a&gt;。 &lt;/p&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style="border-collapse: collapse;"&gt;&lt;hr style="border-top-width: 1px; border-top-color: #CCC; border-top-style: solid; border-bottom-width: 0px; margin: 10px;" /&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style="border-collapse: collapse;"&gt;&lt;table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px;" width="100%"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style="border-collapse: collapse; padding: 0px 10px;"&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;&lt;strong style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;哈佛大学计划&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/nR9-eQhhaJnykcCEGapOHed3uvju2aWlX393MoW8AOLryvGVX4DcWP-2j80NjVm5dl47RVXmRunTUT3FvHGsKOvTUmi6YRCICY-EQ9l3t92bsE094mUiJbWNfP06sL326YGESqJUJfTQjL_K8VgmlJy5zPnJjHbS7A4XYBHTVqQsynAX9MTg_ajZwA-3y07yVWAucF7zJbIN1ZrM9Io5oLRlz8OjPQ-MCp7JbsPjf-PFTOyuTQkCZFRtJDI1Ghfgxj5zl8bJy6fPhPzL16ZlDk8b2_Xbh3cs9hkixBq9IGGdimMD3hZqelLLrZWyM0VXGdtmG7OYkyz4ORqEbSpQji7s6fId1F479NnFfrGgxq9nc9iWC6JnjLbbxEs/wU1a-ZpAfvjkkUC2yCRhoWivS6U0wJL8/7" target="_blank"&gt;从华尔街借入7.5亿美元，&lt;/a&gt;并在特朗普政府对联邦资金的越来越多的威胁中借入。该大学发言人说：“作为一系列财务环境的持续应急计划的一部分，哈佛正在评估提高其学术和研究优先事项所需的资源。”债券文件显示，债务应应纳税，收益将用于一般的公司清算。高盛（Goldman Sachs）是交易的唯一书房。普林斯顿大学还正在&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/F_w4nEecxRixWW_thV9SmCICmnd9YFxTAb8DWuqBRQ0hLsBTTf9xKG2JoSCRzUeAM3NjpsOjU3uE_WUehF6iBvjmQQxMkaPPmOe180DYoFDRT_S28UkDCFEB4dgMpfg7uCHb3yuPVO9gdzhIdYe0P-FOeDplELPdxmdXslSajurMh4R4UUSFmWZvXcBE_4m-FKsgJ4nhbt5HfkxJzcmqQBIMaVmZqKs0X5eRXLGsT8AEkJbab9RcpetqeCUr8M4y4CDljwS1wJIfJw9kqxKuuyTzGaDze8Z0PeOQOA-7nifaO738xEysJrggXnQhUnusAQUgh0k_v0fc1irTZ-tVk8SES0LE94n4wwXn_nBvpAS_36HlYdZqPbT2gEM/KpfTxy5KVFRC6rpwP_clQOd6Jvn7bAuy/7" target="_blank"&gt;考虑&lt;/a&gt;出售应税债券。该学校上周&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/rlk7I-m0NvmrTpnwigWxbwVKDym4I6ZNj77UwrjGVVevBKdptXTPD7-P6T4O48EA0TmkDCr4iHZoJSMCXOm41xOYvGyqhNNeV-K7SL5LN5jl68xwBEendoHoSG0E8Dq3v7rRaBOjKzyN_N9DLgmvnVQG5_FK4PIu9m5PKR1XmiotlyL_uPxg3rsP7S8KLBRyFlsAjoq4goxhnsteawDGYbiI_5tRfd90sB0dKZL0dEWlEknSf6P5jO6i50kIMFnkR2ZjDnIC54LrOmvO90GDXLlNeN85NLeX1kOfcgK6ZNkJdoIuZW9awCQ5j_vRj45JB7MVbapSTHUmxRPLShW_1haO4pQHYKXJq5CaEEjqrifUvNEcTg0DXjdREz8/HajnjaWmbDgSrcwhOfGoVmL8wVP7Eogw/7" target="_blank"&gt;宣布&lt;/a&gt;，美国政府机构已暂停了数十项研究赠款。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div class="body-image" style="margin: 20px 0px;"&gt; &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/vUX8v3k4nR2hCFLjin55qtF5YLwm0lKGpBJmO00E2NnlrQxouMD0yWGpMQqnQMo8kRGD1PHbKgCw3kdkE9XxevUIkth16BZlYyXIky8OdF8FSzQFiVfgMeGQ1mvmbDlfzyyM3FwX8UJbh5X260ACTu3cDHSEbXa7Tc_urkyQ82pK_q8m0blpRyaPyFjzsNN9Go0mP5f8bza8-pfKVPcax87xQxB8kClPo5h82omI9GD2Tv-kVcsAmep_HfruA9J2uuQNZF-Y-JR5CVZsON-Ez50Flgxhrye7dmzhLVNAntboBqct-vjRXf-DblDi_h_VHjfk8_ZqBljL5kpL8V3BjLaUXCC8dkwfQ3bWxy9rEPX-tYAfHDoSxj0KJDY/15jbCcUjG